The**Viewed Product**trigger activates a flow when a contact views a specific product on your website or app.

<Note>
  **Note:** This Trigger is a part of
  [BigCommerce](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/6774740880153-Introduction-and-Installation-of-BigCommerce)
  Integration
</Note>

**Topics Covered:**

- [How to Configure Viewed Product Trigger](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/37780152955161-Viewed-Product#h_01J87E1F8M3AA7MTTXH5ZK1N92)

- [Practical Example](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/37780152955161-Viewed-Product#h_01J87K03NBZ0KHNRZDZ7KVNA9J)

### How to Configure Viewed Product Trigger

- While creating the Trigger Based Flows select**Viewed Product**trigger

![](./Viewed Product – Salesmate_files/mceclip0.png)

- Once the**Viewed Product**trigger is selected, you'll need to configure it by filling in the following details:
  **\*Name:**Assign a clear and descriptive name to identify the trigger.

  **\*Description:**Provide a brief explanation of what the trigger does.

  **\*Select Store:**Choose the BigCommerce store where the cart activity occurs.
  **\*Contact:**Specify any contact properties that need to match before a contact enters this flow.
  **\*BigCommerce:**Set conditions based on product-related properties that must be met before the trigger is activated.

- Once the configuration is completed, hit**Save**.

![](./Viewed Product – Salesmate_files/mceclip1.png)
